I = plt.imread("../data/rose.png")[:, :, :3]
I = no.gray_scale(I)

plt.figure(figsize=(12, 5))

for i in range(8):
    k = 2**i
    lut = no.lut(tur=8, k=k)
    J = no.yogunluk_donusumu(I, LUT=lut)

    plt.subplot(2, 4, i + 1)
    plt.imshow(J)

I = plt.imread("../data/rose.png")[:, :, :3]

J = no.oz_ayrimlilik(I)

plt.figure(figsize=(8, 6))
plt.subplot(2, 2, 1)
plt.imshow(I)

plt.subplot(2, 2, 2)
plt.hist(I.reshape(-1), bins=256, range=(0, 1))

plt.subplot(2, 2, 3)
plt.imshow(J)

plt.subplot(2, 2, 4)
plt.hist(J.reshape(-1), bins=256, range=(0, 1))

plt.show()

In [7]:
I = plt.imread("../data/rose.png")[:, :, :3]

plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))

plt.subplot(2, 2, 1)
h = no.histogram(I, tur=0)
plt.bar(np.linspace(0, 1, 256), h, width=1 / 256, facecolor="red")
plt.title("Red Channel")

plt.subplot(2, 2, 2)
h = no.histogram(I, tur=1)
plt.bar(np.linspace(0, 1, 256), h, width=1 / 256, facecolor="green")
plt.title("Green Channel")

plt.subplot(2, 2, 3)
h = no.histogram(I, tur=2)
plt.bar(np.linspace(0, 1, 256), h, width=1 / 256, facecolor="blue")
plt.title("Blue Channel")

plt.subplot(2, 2, 4)
h = no.histogram(I, tur=3)
plt.bar(np.linspace(0, 1, 256), h, width=1 / 256, facecolor="gray")
plt.title("Grayscale Channel")

plt.show()
